builderTools.legend.PaintBrush.Page1.PlaceBlocks = Place blocks where you're aiming, according to the material you've set
builderTools.legend.PaintBrush.Page1.SelectTargetMaterial = Select targeted material
builderTools.legend.PaintBrush.Page1.AddTargetMaterial = Add targeted material as multi-material
builderTools.legend.PaintBrush.Page1.UndoLastBrush = Undo last brush action
builderTools.legend.PaintBrush.Page1.RedoLastUndo = Redo last undone action
builderTools.legend.PaintBrush.Page1.EditInventoryProperties = Edit materials, size, shape, and other properties from the inventory
