builderTools.legend.PaintBrush.Page2.AxisLock = Axis Lock
builderTools.legend.PaintBrush.Page2.AxisLockDescription = Allows you to stick the brush to a flat, moveable, rotateable surface. The following hotkeys allow you to show, edit, and exit the surface mode.
