builderTools.legend.MachinimaTool.Page7.ToggleDisplay = Toggle editor overlay display
builderTools.legend.MachinimaTool.Page7.TogglePathNodes = Toggle path node visibility
builderTools.legend.MachinimaTool.Page7.ToggleCamera = Toggle camera actor on/off
builderTools.legend.MachinimaTool.Page7.ToggleFrustum = Toggle camera frustum display
builderTools.legend.MachinimaTool.Page7.OriginTitle = Scene Origin Controls:
