builderTools.legend.RulerTool.Page1.SnapToAngles = Hold to enable snapping to 45° angles for precise measurements
builderTools.legend.RulerTool.Page1.DistanceMeasurement = Distance measurements are displayed at each point and along each line segment. Lines are color-coded: Red (X-axis), Green (Y-axis), Blue (Z-axis), White (diagonal)

